Fall In Love.

00:04:29.650 --> 00:04:42.889
Let’s go!

00:04:42.889 --> 00:04:46.419
William handcrafts custom stamps on his Etsy
page SublimingSensation.

00:04:46.419 --> 00:04:51.250
The versatile stamps work with wood burning,
leather burning, and soap melting.

00:04:51.250 --> 00:04:55.090
And he also has a huge variety of custom glass
work.

00:04:55.090 --> 00:05:01.270
Janelle creates a wide variety of step by
step nail art tutorials on her YouTube Channel

00:05:01.270 --> 00:05:02.270
elleandish.

00:05:02.270 --> 00:05:06.830
She creates pop culture characters using nail
stamping as well as making her own stickers

00:05:06.830 --> 00:05:09.560
using sandwich bags and templates.

00:05:09.560 --> 00:05:13.370
Check out her channel to learn how to do this
and a ton of other stuff.

00:05:13.370 --> 00:05:32.800
Here’s Carter with Almost not.

00:05:32.800 --> 00:05:38.520
Danielle Sullivan’s Regrowth is an installation
using books to create a garden including flowers,

00:05:38.520 --> 00:05:40.780
pebbles and even a shed.

00:05:40.780 --> 00:05:45.050
Each item was hand folded and it took two
months to complete.

00:05:45.050 --> 00:05:50.640
RubiArt is a collection of friends in Poland
making portraits out of Rubik’s Cubes - including

00:05:50.640 --> 00:05:53.460
Marilyn Monroe and a Lion.

